{"tid":207877,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"拒從父業走搞笑路線 八両仔望出碟做唱作歌手","createTime":"2017-04-19T07:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T10:46:55.000Z","uid":12709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"236ee1e333c977065853f9cc7ca518ff736f0e79","tid":207877,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:25:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170419&amp;guid=56576975&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170419%26guid%3D56576975%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=4816c4df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170419%26guid%3D56576975%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&h=01361d5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170419&amp;guid=56576975&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n現年22歲嘅星二代八両仔Jacky，要繼承爸爸八両金嘅衣缽入行，不過佢就話唔會走搞笑路線，因為佢想出碟做唱作歌手，仲有意拍埋戲，實行歌影雙棲。<br />\n<br />\n近日染金毛轉新look嘅Jacky，俾網民話同方皓玟同埋MJ（Micheal Jackson)撞樣，Jacky就對似方皓玟冇乜興趣，反而對於講MJ興趣大啲，佢話：「MJ係萬人迷，我好鍾意佢啲歌，佢前無古人，後無來者。」Jacky仲話識跳MJ招牌Moonwalk，即場表演咗一段，Jacky話無師自通，網上自學：「我只係玩玩吓，唔係練咗幾耐，有登台表演吓。」<br />\n<br />\nJacky雖然激讚MJ，但就拒做「港版MJ」：「我鍾意做番自己，我睇下以後喺外國，可唔可以學佢咁接番啲演唱會，似佢好紅、好紅，我想將音樂帶俾觀眾。」Jacky話o依家有跟老竇八両金去吓登台，會唱八両金自己寫嘅歌。<br />\n<br />\n八両金鼓勵Jacky朝唱作歌手目標進發，佢話：「只要唔行衰嗰條路，我一定百分百支持。」即使傾家蕩產都支持囝囝出碟？八両金話：「咁又唔使，我慳啲俾埋佢，只要行正路乜都得。」八両金話Jacky有遠大目標：「我教佢先要有理想，唔可以妄想，夢想要實現，一定要腳踏實地，最後達唔到要求，就要睇開啲。拎錢俾佢出唱片，一步一步嚟，首先佢要自己創作啲歌，寫幾首歌，行咗出去先。」<br />\n<br />\n八両金爆囝囝Jacky稍後有新歌推出，佢會為內地電影《鏍絲釘籃球隊》大唱主題曲《永遠永遠愛着你》，主題係sell激勵，Jacky話：「希望帶出小人物都可以做大事嘅訊息。」<br />\n<br />\nJacky事業上就有明確目標，咁愛情上呢？Jacky話上次拍拖被記者偷拍，火速玩完，o依家冇拍拖亦冇對象，咁佢有乜嘢擇偶條件？Jacky話：「好簡單，一定要交心，我唔睇樣，佢要錫爸爸，尊敬老人家，愛屋及烏，唔使好靚女，你係咪有心水介紹？」Jacky再三強調自己只鍾意異性戀，但唔抗拒身邊人係同性戀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170417/large/1492435723_4a90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170417%2Flarge%2F1492435723_4a90.jpg&h=eb62ab06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170417/large/1492435724_1cde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170417%2Flarge%2F1492435724_1cde.jpg&h=7d688aa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170417/large/1492435726_3193.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170417%2Flarge%2F1492435726_3193.jpg&h=e8ed8c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170417/large/1492435728_8754.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170417%2Flarge%2F1492435728_8754.jpg&h=d0c58d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170417/large/1492435729_86f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170417%2Flarge%2F1492435729_86f2.jpg&h=6f214b0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8516e5dcc02f3b882a4e22827539d7732acb4c2d","tid":207877,"uid":20270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:26:44.000Z","msg":"有錢真好"},{"pid":"8444dd4d4bd74abda7bdea130c3a94c29d3482a9","tid":207877,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:31:23.000Z","msg":"不倫不類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5205d51538b0965a559b0bbbf7232a1c68527d4","tid":207877,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:33:40.000Z","msg":"哪來嘅自信<img src=\"/assets/fac